Grammar

Rule 0     S' -> program
Rule 1     program -> program statement
Rule 2     program -> statement
Rule 3     statement -> assignment
Rule 4     statement -> function_definition
Rule 5     assignment -> ID POW_ASSIGN expression
Rule 6     assignment -> ID INT_DIV_ASSIGN expression
Rule 7     assignment -> ID PLUS_ASSIGN expression
Rule 8     assignment -> ID MINUS_ASSIGN expression
Rule 9     assignment -> ID MULT_ASSIGN expression
Rule 10    assignment -> ID DIV_ASSIGN expression
Rule 11    assignment -> ID MOD_ASSIGN expression
Rule 12    assignment -> ID ASSIGN expression
Rule 13    expression -> STRING
Rule 14    expression -> FLOAT
Rule 15    expression -> INT
Rule 16    expression -> ID
Rule 17    function_definition -> DEF ID LPAREN parameter_list RPAREN COLON INDENT program DENT
Rule 18    parameter_list -> <empty>
Rule 19    parameter_list -> ID
Rule 20    parameter_list -> parameter_list COMMA ID

